cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method for few-shot learning using embeddings and meta-training, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The paper specifically focuses on learning class prototypes in a higher-dimensional space, which is a common technique in machine learning and computer vision.
